Dear {{ object.name }},

Welcome to our Service Marketplace!

Your service provider account has been successfully registered with the following details:


Reference: {{ object.ref }}

Name: {{ object.name }}

Phone: {{ object.provider_phone }}

Contract Period: {{ object.contract_start_date }} to {{ object.contract_expiry_date }}

Service Domains: {{ ', '.join(object.service_domain_ids.mapped('name')) }}

                    {% if object.user_id %}

You can now access your portal account using your phone number as login: {{ object.user_id.login }}

Please check your email for the portal access link.
                    {% endif %}

If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.

Best regards,
Service Marketplace Team
